div.div:
Key Insight: The overlapping 240.0.0.0/8 addresses are never routed across VPCs.
Flow A uses Hybrid NAT to translate them to unique 172.16.x.0/24 IPs before crossing the VPN.
Flow B uses an ILB on a routable /28 subnet — the Envoy proxy (on 241.0.0.0/26) and serverless NEG handle the last hop to Cloud Run internally.
